Project: Mahesh Babu Fan Universe
Website Name: MaheshBabuVerse

🎯 Objective

Build a premium, cinematic, ultra-modern fan website dedicated to Telugu superstar Mahesh Babu.
This should feel like a Marvel / Apple-level experience, not a basic fan page.

The website must be:

Mobile + Desktop optimized

Extremely smooth (60fps animations)

SEO-ready

Highly shareable

Built for future expansion (community, merch, ads, etc.)

🎨 Design Language

Use a cinematic dark theme inspired by Mahesh Babu’s
